ned to our newsletter, social media, and website for updates. If you need to reach GSC staff, please email us at lgbtqa@uic.edu or leave us a voicemail at (312) 413- 3036. Thank you for your patience during these challenging times and be well             Connect with Us        Envelope icon         Subscribe to GSC Newsletter        Speech bubble icon        Contact Us            News            Announcing Lavender Graduation 2020 Keynote Speaker    Posted on March 05, 2020               25 Years of the GSC    Posted on February 12, 2020              Gender and Sexuality Center       Go to slide 1    Go to slide 2    Go to slide 3    Go to slide 4    Go to slide 5    Go to slide 6                Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Articles        LGBTQ Students and the Liberation of College Campuses  Wednesday, February 12, 2020  We hope you can take a moment to read the fabulous piece written by UIC faculty member Jennie Brier entitled “LGBTQ Students and the Liberation of College Campuses.” The GSC is honored to…          UIC Engages Families of LGBTQ Students  Wednesday, February 12, 2020  Check out this article featuring GSC Director JT Turner and Dr. Jennifer Brier, professor of Gender and Women’s Studies and History, talk about the GSC’s Family Acceptance Project: “UIC Engages Families with LGBTQ…              Upcoming Events                Find Us on Social Media     Find Us on Social Media       Find Us on Social Media                        UIC Logo        Gender and Sexuality Center       Contact   1007 W. Harrison St. (MC 369), 181-183, 1180 BSB,  Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 413-8619  lgbtqa@uic.edu     